  "Description": {
    "English": "Specialist <span class=\"name name-technology\">wiring and control threads</span>, this flexible material allows the transmission of power and signals, as well as offering direct manipulation of remote components.<br><br>Used in the creation of a wide range of <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种专业的<span class=\"name name-technology\">线路和控制丝线</span>，这种可弯折的材料允许传输电力和信号，还能提供远程部件的直接操作。<br><br>可用于创造各种<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "專家級<span class=\"name name-technology\">電路與控制線</span>，材質具有彈性，能夠傳輸電力與訊號，也能直接遠端操控元件。<br><br>能用來製造各式<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進科技</span>。"
  },
