  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Hydraulic Wiring from <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Carbon Nanotubes</span>, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span> and <span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span>.<br><br>Craft <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Carbon Nanotubes</span> from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Carbon</span>. Use <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> to craft in empty <span class=\"name name-technology\">Inventory Slots</span>.<br><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span> is readily extracted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">underwater rock deposits</span>. Increase marine efficiency by upgrading the Exosuit <span class=\"name name-technology\">Aeration Membrane</span> or by refilling oxygen supplies from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Kelp Sacs</span>.<br><span class=\"name name-special\">Chromatic Metal</span> is created in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> from the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">stellar metals</span>: <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Copper</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Cadmium</span>, <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Emeril</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Indium</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用<span class=\"name name-commodity\">碳纳米管</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>制作水力线路。<br><br>用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>制作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">碳纳米管</span>。用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空的<span class=\"name name-technology\">库存栏位</span>中制作。<br><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>很容易就能从<span class=\"name name-earth\">水下岩石矿床</span>中提取出来。升级套装<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝气膜</span>或从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，以提高在海洋中的效率。<br><span class=\"name name-special\">有色金属</span>可采用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从<span class=\"name name-stellar\">恒星金属</span>中制得：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">铜</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">镉</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">艾梅里尔</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">铟</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-commodity\">奈米碳管</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>和<span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>製作液壓線路。<br><br>以<span class=\"name name-fuel\">碳</span>製作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">奈米碳管</span>。用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>製作空的<span class=\"name name-technology\">道具欄欄位</span>。<br>可從<span class=\"name name-earth\">水下岩石資源產地</span>萃取<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>。升級強化套裝<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝氣黏膜</span>或從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">巨藻囊</span>補充氧氣補給，以提高海洋行動的效率。<br><span class=\"name name-special\">有色金屬</span>是以<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>加工以下<span class=\"name name-stellar\">星體金屬</span>而成：<span class=\"name name-commodity\">銅</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">鎘</span>、<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">砪</span>、<span class=\"name name-technology\">銦</span>。"
  },
